videos.headline: J. Jackson gets the steal and slams home the dunk

videos.description: Kansas runs the offense to perfection when Frank Mason III finds a cutting Devonte' Graham for the hammer dunk to get the Jayhawks rolling early against Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Graham leading Kansas early with big-time slam

videos.description: 1H (2:03) TTU Zach Smith made Two Point Tip Shot.
videos.headline: Great put back by Texas Tech

videos.description: Josh Jackson shows the quick hands with the steal on the defensive end allowing him to race down the court and finish with an authoritative dunk for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Jackson with the steal and showtime finish
